                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The slacking off of discontinuing the drain line was disappointing to me.  way back when ToT was just the greatest thing known to the class(at least to me when i first got it).  I would like just an extension/upgrade to ToT and manadrain, no need to make it too complicated.  One for return, one for sucking the casting right out of a mob.  the return over time line can stay as it is imo...we have plenty of +mana/tick tricks nowadays, but the lump sum return would be good if...
<br />

<br />
a lvl 60(ish) spell that did 550 return and increased to 600 by 65.  I think that's a reasonable rate.  and a sieve that does 600 straight drain? yea i'd be happy....ToT does 350, and at the time it came out 350 for lvl 52 was a lot more mana than it is nowadays.  
<br />

<br />
/end my 2cp</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=266825" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sydia Vishious</a>
<br />
Coercer of <a href="http://www.fnfguild.com/" target="_blank" class="postlink">Fire and Fury</a>
<br />
Firiona Vie</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
