                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Scryer's Trespass gives you 500 mana and is basically unresistable (-500 check).
<br />
You seem to be asking for essentially the same thing, except with more drain on the mob and faster acting.  As any spell with a 5 minute recast is essentially useless as a mana drain (not sure why we care about draining a mob's mana at the end game anyway) it sounds like you're asking for a spell you already have.
<br />

<br />
Scryer's Trespass is useless as a raid spell, but is actually pretty decent for the new LDoN style dungeons.  Enchanters lacking in the mana regen department will probably find it quite useful.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
